homepage.tipi_chat.default_message.data_: Get data from API and analyze the most popular products

Step 1. Fetch request: https://fakestoreapi.com/carts. Details regarding the returned results:
(1)Array of objects, users' shopping cart lists.
(2)The "products" attribute is an object: (a)"productId": The unique ID of the product. (b)"quantity": The quantity of this product in the cart.

Step 2. Calculate the top 1 "productId" based on the total quantity across all carts.

Step 3. Fetch requests: https://fakestoreapi.com/products/{productId}, {productId} is the result in Step 2. 

Step 4. Send result:

```markdown

### Top 1 product

**Title**: {title}

**Total quantity in carts**: {total quantity}

```
